<nav class="row justify-center header-nav">
  <router-link
    v-if="navTop.length"
    v-for="item in navTop"
    :aria-current="$route.fullPath === item.path ? 'page' : null"
    :key="item.key"
    :to="item.path" 
    :class="`header-nav__link column xs-50 sm-25 header-nav__link--${item.frontmatter.slug}`">
